Package org.mxupdate.update.userinterface

Class Summary
AbstractUIWithFields_mxJPO The class if used to handle fields for web forms and columns for web tables.
AbstractUIWithFields_mxJPO.Field Class used to define a column of a web table or a field of a web form.
Channel_mxJPO The class is used to export and import / update channel configuration items.
Command_mxJPO The class is used to export and import / update command configuration items.
Form_mxJPO The class is used to export, create, delete and update forms within MX.
Inquiry_mxJPO The class is used to export and import / update inquiry configuration items.
Menu_mxJPO The class is used to export and import / update menu configuration items.
Menu_mxJPO.MenuChild Stores a reference to a child of a menu.
Portal_mxJPO The class parses the information about the portal and writes the script used to update portals.
Setting_mxJPO Handles one setting within a user interface object.
Table_mxJPO The class is used to export, create, delete and update tables within MX.
 

Enum Summary
AbstractUIWithFields_mxJPO.Field.SortType Enumeration for the different sort types of a web table column.
